---
title: Lemon-Basil Shrimp Skewers with Orzo & Avocado Salad
description: Summer’s finest produce takes the stage in this delightful dish. Juicy shrimp skewers are topped with a secret ingredient— lemon-basil butter! Marinated tomatoes and creamy avocado make this orzo salad something special.
